    {
      "id": "value_propositions",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Value Propositions\n- Λιγότερα λάθη παραγγελιών & γρηγορότερο service.\n- Offline fallback για αξιοπιστία παντού.\n- Commission-based ή χαμηλό SaaS (μειωμένο ρίσκο).\n- App-less εμπειρία για τον πελάτη (Web/PWA).\n[[business/market_strategy.md]]\n[[pitch/deck.md]]",
      "x": 100,
      "y": -300,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 450
    },
    {
      "id": "customer_relationships",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Customer Relationships\n- B2B: Self-serve onboarding (για small venues).\n- B2B: Dedicated account manager (Enterprise/Festivals).\n- B2C: Zero interaction, pure utility.",
      "x": 450,
      "y": -300,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 200
    },
    {
      "id": "channels",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Channels\n- Direct B2B Sales (Πόρτα-πόρτα αρχικά).\n- Word of Mouth / Παρευρισκόμενοι σε φεστιβάλ.\n- Digital Marketing (B2B SaaS focus).",
      "x": 450,
      "y": -50,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 200
    },
    {
      "id": "customer_segments",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Customer Segments\n**B2B:**\n- Beach Bars & Resort Bars\n- Food Festivals & Events\n- Self-service Cafes / Bistros\n**B2C:**\n- Τελικοί καταναλωτές που μισούν τις ουρές.\n[[business/model.md]]",
      "x": 800,
      "y": -300,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 450
    },
    {
      "id": "cost_structure",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Cost Structure\n- Cloud Hosting (AWS/GCP)\n- Hardware costs (αν τα παρέχουμε εμείς)\n- R&D / Μισθοδοσία\n- Marketing & Sales commissions\n- Payment Gateway Fees",
      "x": -600,
      "y": 200,
      "width": 650,
      "height": 200
    },
    {
      "id": "revenue_streams",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Revenue Streams\n- SaaS Συνδρομές (Tiers: Free/Basic/Pro)\n- Commission model (3-5% επί των παραγγελιών)\n- Setup fees / Hardware Sales (αν εφαρμόζεται)\n[[business/pricing_model.md]]",
      "x": 100,
      "y": 200,
      "width": 1000,
      "height": 200
    },
    {
